#

Cottage Cheese and Cucumber Salad

10 min
$5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbVegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthyLight meal

Description

A refreshing and protein-packed salad that's perfect for a light meal or snack!

Ingredients

  • cottage cheese: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium, diced
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped (optional)
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon (optional)
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon (optional)
